abstract: NAVESINK, N. J., July 15 In All Saints Memorial  Church (Episcopal) this afternoon, Miss Susan Wheeler Davenport, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. John Davenport of New York, became the bride of Piers Leighton Brooke of London. He is the son of Lady Mabel Cheatham of Mexico City and Eyford Park, Gloucestershire, England, wife of Sir Nicolas Cheatham, British Ambassador to Mexico, and of Richard N. Brooke of Hamburg, Germany, and Nice, France.
